tsdb.graph.processing

Class Interpolated

  • java.lang.Object
    • tsdb.graph.node.Continuous.Abstract
      • tsdb.graph.processing.Interpolated
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Continuous, Node
    Deprecated.

    @Deprecated
public class Interpolated
extends Continuous.Abstract
    This node tries to interpolate missing values. For one-values gaps it uses linear interpolation. For bigger gaps it uses multilinear interpolation.
